    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "FEDERAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "I am extremely interested in the [REDACTED] and I will",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "be most grateful if you could help clear up the mystery in this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "affair. The reason I am writing you is because I have learned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "recently that a researcher of the flying saucer mystery said the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "FBI is involved in this affair.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "A civilian investigating agency was formed in Bridgeport,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Conn., in 1952, to look into the flying saucer mystery by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] He called the organization [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED] And, during his study of the saucer mystery",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] ran across something important. This information was",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "evidently the solution to the mystery for in 1953 [REDACTED] stated",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "bluntly, \"I know what the saucers are.\" Then, \"three men in black",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "suits\" silenced him. Even today [REDACTED] will not discuss the matter",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "of his \"hush-up\" with anyone. However, I have learned that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "secret of the saucers lies the \"dreadful underground menace\" that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "is threatening the world. And, I am also extremely interested in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "this \"menace.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "I have some very important information concerning this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "\"dreadful underground menace\" that I would like to discuss with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "[REDACTED] very much. For the story concerning this \"menace\" is",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "certainly a \"hellish Horror\" one, which reveals a fantastic",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "situation, so fantastic, that it would be hardly conceivable by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "the public. Yes indeed, I would appreciate it very much if you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "could help me get in touch with [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "I have also been getting information regarding \"certain\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "ship tragedies that have occurred on the high seas for a very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "long time, and \"certain\" aircraft accidents and disappearances.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "For these tragedies reveal evidence that gives proof that such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "a \"menace\" really \"exists.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "I certainly will be looking forward in hearing from you.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
